snippet.textDisplay:
It's weird, but I was absolutely ready to attribute this track to being from a fan game. Can't help but think "I Wanna Be The Guy" when I hear it. 

It's one of those things where you make a connection the first time you hear something and it sticks. The original version of a song will sound like a remix if you heard a remix first for example.
